  • Description: PLASTIC 5 GALLON BUCKET WITH A CORROSIVE DIAMOND LABEL AND MULTI-PART FORM HAZMAT PAPERS WAS FOUND LEAKING NEAR THE IREG-6 BELT ON THE FLOOR. PROCESSED THE CORROSIVE LIQUID USING SODIUM BICARBONATE AND ZEP ZORBENT.
